	R1. The system must process a LOPD update or modification.	
	R1.1. The administrator must analyze the LOPD changes when the message "lOPD changed" is received.	
	R1.2. The administrator must cancel the gateway until further notice if the gateway changes are not accepted.	
	R1.3. The administrator must make gateway changes if the gateway changes are accepted.	
	R1.4. The administrator must notify the changes in LOPD and the gateway to the education center.	
	R1.5. The education center's responsible must analyze the gateway changes.	
	R1.6. The education center's responsible must analyze the LOPD changes.	
	

